cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.CY 

This paper discusses a system for detecting account theft in online games, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed system uses action sequence analysis, which involves machine learning techniques such as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.LG). The system also involves software engineering (cs.SE) in terms of implementing security measures on the server-side. Additionally, the paper discusses tracing stolen money, which could fall under the category of cybercrime (cs.CY).
